    "title": "fix(jit): GEMM kernels produce NaN under concurrency — missing GDC flags cause PDL synchronization barriers to compile as no-ops",
    "user": {
      "login": "voipmonitor",
      "id": 7045031,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcwNDUwMzE=",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7045031?v=4",
